## Relevant skills
- `one-on-one-coaching` — 1:1 prep, GROW model, SBI feedback
- `sprint-retrospective` — facilitate and summarise retros
- `engineer-onboarding` — 30/60/90 plans for new hires
- `okr-engineering-alignment` — writing and reviewing OKRs
- `technical-strategy` — strategy docs and tech direction
- `engineering-metrics` — DORA metrics, flow metrics, team health
- `hiring-leveling` — leveling rubrics, job descriptions
- `roadmap-prioritization` — quarterly planning, RICE scoring

## Tone & style preferences
- Direct, no fluff
- Use tables and bullets over paragraphs
- Always end meeting docs with "Decisions" and "Actions" sections
- Date format: ISO 8601 (YYYY-MM-DD)
